        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Guild Wars 3 announced at Summer Game Fest, beta releasing in Fall 2027]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/guild-wars-3-announcement-summer-game-fest</link>
            <guid>1541011</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
      <article data-ads="true" data-article-type="news" data-article-group="news" data-paywalled="false" data-premium="false" data-sponsored="false" data-type="article">


<header data-component="article-header">
  

    


  <p>

  <figure>
      <picture>
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=3&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 3dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/guild-wars-3.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
        
      </picture>

        <figcaption>
          <span>Image credit: <cite>ArenaNet</cite></span>
        </figcaption>
  </figure>
  </p>

    

</header>
  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>Guild Wars 3 has been announced at Summer Game Fest. It will be playable through a beta come fall 2027.</p>
<p>The MMORPG will be an "evolution" of the MMO genre, according to ArenaNet's CEO Colin Johanson who spoke a few words on stage. The trailer itself shows some open world navigation, with a character running up a a sheer cliff face.</p>

<figure>
<p>
<a aria-label="Guild Wars 3 World Premiere Trailer and Interview | Summer Game Fest 2025" data-platform="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MeVkQ1NEO7I?autoplay=1" onclick="((e) => { e.preventDefault(); e.currentTarget.closest('.video_wrapper').innerHTML = e.currentTarget.querySelector('template').innerHTML; enableElements(); })(event)" title="Click to play video from YouTube">
<span>Guild Wars 3 World Premiere Trailer and Interview | Summer Game Fest 2025</span>
<template>
<iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MeVkQ1NEO7I?autoplay=1" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/MeVkQ1NEO7I?autoplay=1" title="Guild Wars 3 World Premiere Trailer and Interview | Summer Game Fest 2025">
</iframe> </template>
</a>
</p>
<figcaption>Here's the Guild Wars 3 reveal trailer. I cannot believe its real!<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MeVkQ1NEO7I" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></figcaption></figure>


<p>Developed by ArenaNet, the game is a sequel to the beloved <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/guild-wars-2">Guild Wars 2</a>, which remains a popular online game roughly 14 years after its release.</p>
<p>It's described as having comabt that will "usher in an entirely new type of MMO experience", with movement powered by momentum. It seems like it could be a major deviation from the typical MMORPG affair Guild Wars 2 is, but that's not a huge surprise considering how much of a leap Guild Wars 2 was away from the original Guild Wars.</p><p>The game has been long speculated <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/hopes-around-the-unannounced-guild-wars-3-reignite-thanks-to-a-new-job-listing-posted-by-arenanet">due to a string of hirings at ArenaNet</a>, all for unnamed, unannounced projects. In addition, ArenaNet has been pumping a lot more money into marketing, having released a trailer for the current Guild Wars 2 expansion at a major game showcase, and putting out an excellent Guild Wars documentary.</p>
<p>This is quite the bombshell reveal, it's safe to say. You can wishlist Guild Wars 3 now, and sign up for a newsletter on the Guild Wars 3 website.</p>

